<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app="ravada.app">
%= include 'bootstrap/header'
<body id="page-top" data-spy="scroll" data-target=".navbar-fixed-top" role="document">
    <div id="wrapper">
    <div ng-controller="requirements">
    %= include 'bootstrap/navigation'
    <div id="page-wrapper">

        <!--BASES AND DOMAINS LIST-->

            <div class="page-header">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <hr>
                            <h2 class="text-center"><%=l 'Requirements' %></h2>
								                <i class="fa fa-linux fa-3x " aria-hidden="true"> GNU/Linux</i><br><p> For spice redirection you'll need to install <a target=_blank href="https://virt-manager.org/download/">VirtViewer<i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> in your computer.<br>
                                Search in your distro, e.g. in Debian/Ubuntu with <i><b>sudo apt-get install virt-viewer</b></i></p>

                                <i class="fa fa-windows  fa-3x" aria-hidden="true"> Microsoft Windows </i>&copy;<br><p> You'll need to install <a target=_blank href="https://virt-manager.org/download/">VirtViewer<i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>, e.g. VirtViewer v5.0-256 in your computer.</p>
                                <p>Be aware that in Windows, spice redirection is not automatically. It's necessary associate protocol with the app.<br>
                                To make this possible, download <a target=_blank href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UPC/ravada/master/docs/spice.reg">regfile <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> or copy the following lines in an ASCII file and save with extension .reg, then execute the file.<br>
                                <code>

                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice]<br>
                                @="URL:spice"<br>
                                "URL Protocol"=""<br>
                                <br>
                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice\DefaultIcon]<br>
                                @="C:\\Program Files\\VirtViewer v5.0-256\\bin\\remote-viewer.exe,1"<br>
                                <br>
                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice\Extensions]
                                <br>
                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice\shell]<br>
                                @="open"<br>
                                <br>
                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice\shell\open]<br>
                                [HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\spice\shell\open\command]<br>
                                @="\"C:\\Program Files\\VirtViewer v5.0-256\\bin\\remote-viewer.exe\" \"%1\""<br></code></p>

                                <i class="fa fa-apple fa-3x " aria-hidden="true"> OS X</i>&copy;<br><p> For spice redirection you'll need to install <a target=_blank href="http://people.freedesktop.org/~teuf/spice-gtk-osx/dmg/0.5.7/RemoteViewer-0.5.7-1.dmg">RemoteViewer <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> in your computer.<br></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    %= include 'bootstrap/scripts'
